fgeo.x 0.0.0.9000
  • Reference
  • fgeo

Tiny ForestGEO datasets for examples

Installation

Install the development version of fgeo.x with:

# install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("forestgeo/fgeo.x")

Or install all fgeo packages in one step.

For details on how to install packages from GitHub, see this article.

Example

library(fgeo.x)

glimpse_structure <- function(x, n = length(x)) {
  str(x, list.len = n, give.attr = FALSE)
}

glimpse_structure(elevation)
